{"sha": "19429ce132d8cc9526ab4fe46d6287f2ad89ef1c", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0NzI0NzEyOjE5NDI5Y2UxMzJkOGNjOTUyNmFiNGZlNDZkNjI4N2YyYWQ4OWVmMWM=", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Ian Jackson", "email": "ijackson@chiark.greenend.org.uk", "date": "2021-04-22T14:05:23Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Ian Jackson", "email": "ijackson@chiark.greenend.org.uk", "date": "2021-05-07T10:17:44Z"}, "message": "panic ui test: Improve error handling\n\nPrevioously, if somehow this program got a wrong argument, it would\npanic in the re-executed child.  But that looks like a \"success\"\nfor this program!  We mustn't panic unless everything is great.\n\nSigned-off-by: Ian Jackson <ijackson@chiark.greenend.org.uk>", "tree": {"sha": "606d5f9ceadea41f9b9115ecbea6fac2c7da06e0", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/trees/606d5f9ceadea41f9b9115ecbea6fac2c7da06e0"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/git/commits/19429ce132d8cc9526ab4fe46d6287f2ad89ef1c", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/19429ce132d8cc9526ab4fe46d6287f2ad89ef1c", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/commit/19429ce132d8cc9526ab4fe46d6287f2ad89ef1c", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/commits/19429ce132d8cc9526ab4fe46d6287f2ad89ef1c/comments", "author": {"login": "ijackson", "id": 2090772, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjIwOTA3NzI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2090772?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/ijackson", "html_url": "https://github.com/ijackson", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ijackson/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ijackson/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ijackson/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/ijackson/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://ap